list.abstract: before，英语单词，可用作副词、连接词与介词，翻译为先于、过去等。

yingyinNormal.en: Or one of his previous targets is coming back for revenge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也或许是他之前的某个目标回来报仇了。

yingyinNormal.en: Miss Clark, why should I employ you, instead of, say, the previous candidate?
yingyinNormal.zh: 克拉克小姐，我为什么要雇佣你，而不是之前来面试的人？

yingyinNormal.en: By dusk the sorrows of the previous year have been well and truly washed away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 日薄西山，先前的悲伤苦痛已被彻底洗净。

yingyinNormal.en: You're happier for a little bit, because you still remember your previous house.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你暂时是满足的因为你还记得之前的房子。

yingyinNormal.en: Many of this year's winners spoke of being inspired by athletes of previous generations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今年很多的奖牌得主都说受到了前辈运动员们的鼓舞。

yingyinNormal.en: Cities have been built to a size and scale not matched in any previous period in world history.
yingyinNormal.zh: 建成城市的大小和规模前无古人。

yingyinNormal.en: Previous experience next to zero. Yet, he has a recommend letter from our board. W.T.F. to that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 之前的工作经历几乎为零，但是却有我们董事会的推荐信，这特么真稀奇。

yingyinNormal.en: Up until recently, they did not know Alicia, and had no encounters with her in a previous location.
yingyinNormal.zh: 到现在为止，他们不了解艾丽西娅，也没有在其他地方相处过。

yingyinNormal.en: That is enough. Tell me, do you have access to your previous configuration? Yes. Access that, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可以了，告诉我，你能接入先前的配置吗？是的。请接入吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Do these pleasing attentions proceed from the impulse of the moment or are they the result of previous study?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但你这种讨人喜欢的奉承话是临时想起来的呢，还是老早想好了的？

yingyinNormal.en: All right, without objection, the minutes of the previous date are considered read and agreed to. Any new business?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，如无异议，上一次约会的概要记录就算是已经阅毕并同意通过了。有什么新事宜吗？

yingyinNormal.en: This foundation is something I bought a few months ago when I realized that my previous foundation was just completely off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个粉底是我几个月前买的，那时我发现之前的粉底已经用完了。

yingyinNormal.en: I realize that my previous employment with my brother might not be directly applicable. However, I am abnormally organized.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道我之前在我哥哥手下的工作经历可能和这份工作不是很相符，可是我这人做事条理分明。

yingyinNormal.en: Given this situation, I have no choice but to withdraw my previous objections to your ill-considered relationship with Leonard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在看来，无奈之下我只能收回我之前对你和莱纳德关系的反对。

yingyinNormal.en: Your previous employer, here, says you are a warm, chatty and life-enhancing presence with a lot of potential. Yes, I paid him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的上任雇主说你是一个热心，健谈，让人难忘，拥有无限潜力的人。对，我贿赂他让他这么说的。

yingyinNormal.en: Abernathy and Walter were exhibiting other aberrancies beyond memory recall of previous builds. They were hearing voices. Talking to someone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾伯纳西和沃尔特出现了其他异常现象，不仅仅是回忆起先前的故事设定，他们还出现了幻听，与人对话。

yingyinNormal.en: When I applied, in my resume, I told them that I worked as a VP of Information Technology at a previous company. But there was no VP of Information Technology.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我应聘的时候简历上曾写到，我在之前的公司做的是信息安全副总，但实际上我没做过信息安全副总。

yingyinNormal.en: The Fed uses vast amounts of economic data to determine how much currency should be in circulation, including previous rates of inflation, international trends, and the unemployment rate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 联准会透过大量的经济数据来决定流通的货币数量，这些数据包括过去的通膨率，国际趋势以及失业率。
